Package: pilr.api.r
Title: Interact with PiLR servers via the API
Description: The pilr.api.r package allows users to interact with PiLR Health
    servers through a friendly R interface. This is especially useful when
    writing your own Data Processing Units (DPUs) for your PiLR projects.
Version: 0.1
Authors: Erik Iverson (eiverson@meinergy.net)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2),
    httr (>= 0.3),
    jsonlite (>= 0.9.7)
Imports:
